2.3.0
    - **BREAKING CHANGES**
        - Depreciate `bg-color-light-error` mixin
        - Depreciate `row-reverse` mixin, renamed to `direction-row-reverse`
        - Depreciate `position-context` mixin, renamed to `position-relative`
        - Depreciate `text-all-caps` mixin, renamed to `text-uppercase`
    - **Change mixins**
        - `border` mixin, now use `$border-color` variable to allow to change border colors
        - `text-normal` mixin, small tweak to use `base-text-weight` mixin.
        - `text-quiet` mixin, small tweak to use `$font-size` value rather than `0.785em`
        - `text-bold` mixin, small tweak to use `base-text-weight` mixin
    - **New mixins**
        - background color mixins: `bg-color-neutral-00`, `bg-color-neutral-10`, `bg-color-neutral-15`, `bg-color-neutral-20`, `bg-color-neutral-40`, `bg-color-neutral-50`, `bg-color-neutral-60`, `bg-color-neutral-70`, `bg-color-brand`, `bg-color-accent`, `bg-color-primary-action`, `bg-color-secondary-action`, and `bg-color-success`
        - box shadow mixin: `box-shadow`
        - color mixins: `color-neutral-00`, `color-neutral-10`, `color-neutral-15`, `color-neutral-20`, `color-primary-action`, `color-secondary-action`, `color-sale`
        - display mixins: `display`, `display-inline-block`, `display-inline`, `display-none`
        - flexbox mixins: `direction-column`, `direction-column-reverse`, `direction-row`, `direction-row-reverse`, `flex-none`
        - heading mixins: `heading-level-1`, `heading-level-2`, `heading-level-3`, `heading-level-4`, `heading-level-5`, `heading-level-6`
        - layout mixins: `position-relative`, `position-absolute`, `position-fixed`, `position-top`, `position-right`, `position-bottom`, `position-left`, `position-full`, `base-bleed`
        - text mixins: `base-font-family`, `text-font-family`, `text-header-font-family`, `text-loaded-header-font-family`, `base-text-weight`, `text-thin`, `text-extra-light`, `text-light`, `text-regular`, `text-medium`, `text-semi-bold`, `base-text-size`, `text-size-smaller`, `text-size-small`, `text-size-normal`, `text-size-big`, `text-size-bigger`, `text-size-huge`, `line-height`, `letter-spacing`, `text-uppercase`
        - z-index mixin: `z-index`
2.2.0
    - Add text-lowercase mixin
    - Add width-full-block mixin
    - Update width-full mixin
2.1.0
    - Add text-capitalize
    - Change tag version step in RELEASE.md
2.0.1
    - Fix typos in colors utilities
    - Cleanup README.md to remove outdated content, and add new relevant content
    - Ignore npm log files
    - Add release instructions in RELEASE.md
2.0.0
    - Prepare Spline for distribution on NPM
    - Remove all references to Bower
    - Add Github PR template
    - Add linting
    - Add CircleCI integration
    - Add new utility mixins
    - Remove outdated features (CSS3 mixins)
1.0.0
    - Requires Sass 3.4
    - Added a desktop override mixin (see utilities/_style-override)
    - Rewrote web-font mixin for better font-family support
0.4.1
    - Fixed issue with `$font-formats` not providing the right format name for Truetype fonts.
0.4.0
    - Rename `icon-font-content` function to `icon-address`.
    - Add a `cache-buster` function to generate a cache-busting string at the end of a URL.
    - Include `cache-buster` in the `icon-font` mixin as an optional flag.
0.3.1
    - Fix syntax error with `ellipsis` mixin.
    - Remove `no-wrap` option from `ellipsis` mixin.
    - Re-add missing `change-br` mixin to the Spline import file.
0.3.0
    - Split the old `icon-font` mixin into discrete files.
    - Add a new `web-font` mixin to make including web fonts easier.
0.2.2
    - `tap-highlight` mixin no longer relies on the non-existent `$margin` variable.
    - `clearfix` mixin now acts more consistently with how `overflow: hidden` works.
0.2.1
    - Updated clearfix mixin to match behaviour with `overflow: hidden`. Should now contain margins instead of collapsing them.
0.2.0
    - Add `reverse-gradient()` function.
0.1.1
    - Add `rem()` function
0.1.0
    - Initial release

For a more detailed changelog, see: https://github.com/mobify/spline/releases
